  "description": {
    "S": "This easy Slow Cooker Chicken Tikka Masala is packed with warm, aromatic flavor from a blend of Indian spices, fresh ginger, and garlic - all coming together in a rich, creamy tomato sauce with tender chicken thighs. Simple to prepare, deeply satisfying."
  },
